Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}性懲りも無く Fight 仲間と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I won't run away from my sin no more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:07.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何処までも抗って Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:10.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 超えていく 恐れずに Bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not afraid, bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if I'm drown in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分のチカラに変え Wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 捻じ曲げる System
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never ever follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:29.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 立ち向かう and I'll defeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像人性一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:20.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你将凝视深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:26.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你踏入其中 你会发觉自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.31,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}踏入未知领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:31.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那些漂亮话 早就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.50,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人得以为人的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:37.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总是伴随着我们 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.51,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}致命的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不要转移视线 赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只是向前 向前 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:43.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须再次取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.23,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}代价在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使前方是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不再有任何后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.62,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坠落 坠落 堕入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.17,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是 永远不回头 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.14,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}高举烽烟 然后潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与烦恼说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惩前毖后 与伙伴一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}活着就是为了择日赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.67,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再逃避我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:07.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我将一直抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:10.67,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 无畏地超越 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不害怕 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使我将陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要将其转化为我的力量 消除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 扭曲这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.09,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.30,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:29.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 我将面对挑战并战胜自己
